&gt; Hi Rocco,
&gt; 
&gt; Yes, that&#39;s what I would expect when all assumptions fail.
&gt; 
&gt; What happens when it&#39;s not a theory and an assumption is used 
&gt; and fails would have to depend on whether you want to support 
&gt; / encourage that use.
&gt; 
&gt; Charlie
&gt; 
